      • usage

        public String usage()
        Description copied from interface: Operation
        Method to allow commands the option to override the default usage from jcommander where all the fields are printed out in alphabetical order. Some classes may want to put the basic/required fields first, with optional fields at the bottom, or however other custom usage's would be necessary.

        If method returns null, the default usage from jcommander is used
